data.description:
2.972% Assumable $253k Mortgage Available!!! That's right! Under 3% interest rate available in 2023 with no mortgage insurance and no loan origination fees.
 
Assumable rate available now to VA and non-VA qualified buyers. For more info on the loan please contact Xander Gregory Directly.

Welcome to Casa Fiesta Townhouses.  Built in the 1960's this unit and community boast a lot of original charm.
 
Conveniently located just 10mins from Central Phoenix and 10mins from The Biltmore and Arcadia areas, commuting is a breeze.  
  
The townhouse is situated brilliantly within the community, there are no neighbors directly in front or behind the property.  Outside the front door is a private park with grass and mature trees. Walk over the park and within 30 seconds you'll be at the community pool. Please see drone footage of the house and community on the MLS, alternatively if you do not have access to the MLS please contact one of the listing agents and we will send you the footage directly.  
  
This property is a clean-slate desperate for somebody to love it and make it their own.
